Upgrading to Angular 15
https://levelup.gitconnected.com/angular-upgrade-26d331837012
The new Angular release came with a support for 
Node.js versions 14.20.x, 16.13.x, and 18.10.x. 
node --version

Step 1: Upgrade TypeScript

Check which packages have newer versions available: 
npm outdated

To update just the typescript dependency to version 4.8.4: 
npm install typescript@4.8.4